Package: ClimClass
Type: Package
Title: Climate Classification according to several indices
Version: 1.0
Date: 2014-10-13
Author: Emanuele Eccel, Emanuele Cordano, Giambattista Toller
Maintainer: Emanuele Eccel <emanuele.eccel@fmach.it>
Description: Classification of climate according to Koeppen - Geiger, of
    aridity indices, of continentality indices, and of water balance after
    Thornthwaite. Drawing climographs: Thornthwaite, Peguy, Bagnouls-Gaussen,
    Walter-Lieth.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends:
    R(>= 2.10.0),geosphere,ggplot2,reshape2
Suggests:
    climatol
